# Component Guidelines

## Component Structure
- Use `script setup` syntax
- Use `style scoped` syntax
- Keep components focused and small
- Use proper component composition
- Implement proper prop validation
- Use proper event handling

## Component Communication
- Use proper props and events
- Implement proper state management
- Use proper component lifecycle
- Implement proper component testing
- Use proper component documentation

## Component Reusability
- Create reusable components
- Use proper component composition
- Implement proper component testing
- Use proper component documentation
- Implement proper component versioning

## Component Performance
- Use proper component lifecycle
- Implement proper component caching
- Use proper component lazy loading
- Implement proper component testing
- Use proper component optimization

## When to Apply
- When creating new components
- When refactoring existing components
- When implementing component features
- When reviewing component code
- When testing components 